description:
KTT is Kringle Trade Token, an ERC 20 token tethered to the Kringle,  the smallest unit of The Billion Coin ( TBC)

KTT is a solution to the persistent issue of liquidity of the abundance-based coin which is not on public exchanges and not exchangeable.

KTT is a multifaceted stable token created to maintain its stability by virtue of community agreement and the strong use cases, guaranteeing its liquidity.
name: Kringle Trade Token
